        "description": "A private email service API that provides secure email management with domain-based configuration, encrypted storage, and developer-friendly endpoints.\n\nMailVault allows users to:\n- Manage custom domains for email services\n- Create and configure email addresses with forwarding and catch-all options\n- Send emails via API using domain API keys\n- Receive and store encrypted emails\n- Access received emails through secure endpoints\n\n## Authentication\nThe API uses JWT tokens for user authentication. Some endpoints require API keys for domain-specific operations.\n\n## Rate Limiting\nAPI endpoints are rate limited to prevent abuse. See individual endpoint documentation for specific limits.",
